    <div class="column-two-thirds">
      <h2 class="gem-c-heading  gem-c-heading--padding gem-c-heading--margin-bottom-2  ">Featured</h2>

    </div>
  </div>

      <div class="gem-c-image-card gem-c-image-card--large brand--hm-treasury">
    <figure class="gem-c-image-card__image-wrapper"><img class="gem-c-image-card__image" alt="Balloons GAD 100" src="https://assets.publishing.service.gov.uk/government/uploads/system/uploads/feature/image/68741/s712_Balloons_343246_960_640.jpg"></img></figure>

    <div class="gem-c-image-card__text-wrapper">
      <p class="gem-c-image-card__context"><time datetime="2019-02-05"> 5 February 2019</time><span aria-hidden="true"> — </span>News story</p>

        <h3 class="gem-c-image-card__title">
              <a class="gem-c-image-card__title-link brand__color" href="/government/news/the-government-actuarys-department-marks-its-centenary">The Government Actuary’s Department marks its centenary</a>
</h3>
      <div class="gem-c-image-card__description"><div class="govspeak">
<p>The Government Actuary’s Department (GAD) is 100 years old this year. The department is marking its centenary with the ‘GAD100’ programme where we will mark our successes and highlight our role in government.</p>
</div></div>


    </div>
  </div>


